Jay_Paterno\", \"score\": 0.7695312248220336, \"rank\": 0.2994924266463329, \"text\": \"Paterno\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jay_Paterno\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jay_Paterno\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am in high school in Colorado, and my mom's like, 'Joe Paterno's on the phone,'\\\" Hovasse said.\", \"from\": 2810, \"to\": 2907, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2834, \"end\": 2842, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colorado_Buffaloes_men's_basketball\", \"score\": 0.8523277133073451, \"rank\": 0.173255060609021, \"text\": \"Colorado\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colorado_Buffaloes_men's_basketball\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colorado_Buffaloes_men's_basketball\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"high school\", \"from\": 2819, \"to\": 2830}, {\"ngram\": \"my mom\", \"from\": 2848, \"to\": 2854}, {\"ngram\": \"the phone\", \"from\": 2881, \"to\": 2890}, {\"ngram\": \"Hovasse\", \"from\": 2894, \"to\": 2901}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I thought, 'What?'\", \"from\": 2908, \"to\": 2927, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Because I loved Penn State football.\", \"from\": 2928, \"to\": 2964, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2944, \"end\": 2954, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penn_State_Nittany_Lions_basketball\", \"score\": 0.9999988761252956, \"rank\": 7.416176123642831e-07, \"text\": \"Penn State\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penn_State_Nittany_Lions_basketball\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penn_State_Nittany_Lions_basketball\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And then I said, 'Man, Penn State's not very good, but I have a chance to play my freshman year, and I love that.\", \"from\": 2965, \"to\": 3078, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a chance\", \"from\": 3027, \"to\": 3035}, {\"ngram\": \"my freshman year\", \"from\": 3044, \"to\": 3060}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yeah, I want to do that.'\\\"\", \"from\": 3079, \"to\": 3105, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In 1986, Hovasse and Parkhill began their up-and-down relationship.\", \"from\": 3107, \"to\": 3174, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hovasse\", \"from\": 3116, \"to\": 3123}, {\"ngram\": \"Parkhill\", \"from\": 3128, \"to\": 3136}, {\"ngram\": \"their up-and-down relationship\", \"from\": 3143, \"to\": 3173}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Parkhill was demanding, and Hovasse did not always take that well.\", \"from\": 3175, \"to\": 3241, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Parkhill\", \"from\": 3175, \"to\": 3183}, {\"ngram\": \"Hovasse\", \"from\": 3203, \"to\": 3210}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For instance, Hovasse thought he played pretty good defense in high school.\", \"from\": 3242, \"to\": 3317, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"instance\", \"from\": 3246, \"to\": 3254}, {\"ngram\": \"Hovasse\", \"from\": 3256, \"to\": 3263}, {\"ngram\": \"pretty good defense\", \"from\": 3282, \"to\": 3301}, {\"ngram\": \"high school\", \"from\": 3305, \"to\": 3316}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Parkhill did not and broke down every aspect of the 6-8 forward's defensive game as soon as Hovasse arrived in State College.\", \"from\": 3318, \"to\": 3443, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3429, \"end\": 3442, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penn_State_Nittany_Lions\", \"score\": 0.7029598583528304, \"rank\": 0.4224980674928773, \"text\": \"State College\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penn_State_Nittany_Lions\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penn_State_Nittany_Lions\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Parkhill\", \"from\": 3318, \"to\": 3326}, {\"ngram\": \"every aspect\", \"from\": 3350, \"to\": 3362}, {\"ngram\": \"the 6-8 forward's defensive game\", \"from\": 3366, \"to\": 3398}, {\"ngram\": \"Hovasse\", \"from\": 3410, \"to\": 3417}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Yeah, it was hard,\\\" Hovasse said.\", \"from\": 3445, \"to\": 3479, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hovasse\", \"from\": 3466, \"to\": 3473}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was a tough four years.\", \"from\": 3480, \"to\": 3507, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a tough four years\", \"from\": 3488, \"to\": 3506}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He wanted me to redshirt my senior year [because of an injury], and there was no way I was redshirting my senior year.\", \"from\": 3508, \"to\": 3626, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an injury\", \"from\": 3560, \"to\": 3569}, {\"ngram\": \"no way\", \"from\": 3586, \"to\": 3592}, {\"ngram\": \"my senior year\", \"from\": 3611, \"to\": 3625}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was not staying five years.\\\"\", \"from\": 3627, \"to\": 3657, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yes, Parkhill said, he was tough.\", \"from\": 3659, \"to\": 3692, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Parkhill\", \"from\": 3664, \"to\": 3672}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He thought he had to be, since Penn State could not recruit the high-profile players and McDonald's All-Americans.\", \"from\": 3693, \"to\": 3807, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3724, \"end\": 3734, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penn_State_Nittany_Lions_basketball\", \"score\": 0.9999988761252956, \"rank\": 7.416176123642831e-07, \"text\": \"Penn State\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penn_State_Nittany_Lions_basketball\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penn_State_Nittany_Lions_basketball\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the high-profile players\", \"from\": 3753, \"to\": 3777}, {\"ngram\": \"McDonald's All-Americans\", \"from\": 3782, \"to\": 3806}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Still, Hovasse flourished with the Nittany Lions.\", \"from\": 3808, \"to\": 3857, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3843, \"end\": 3856, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penn_State_Nittany_Lions_basketball\", \"score\": 0.9999949747951931, \"rank\": 3.780467184735569e-06, \"text\": \"Nittany Lions\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penn_State_Nittany_Lions_basketball\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penn_State_Nittany_Lions_basketball\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hovasse\", \"from\": 3815, \"to\": 3822}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He led the team in scoring and rebounding from 1987-89, was named first-team all-Atlantic 10 in 1989 and was a two-time team MVP.\", \"from\": 3858, \"to\": 3987, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3983, \"end\": 3986, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Most_valuable_player\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.5600633311078855e-14, \"text\": \"MVP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Most_valuable_player\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Most_valuable_player\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 3865, \"to\": 3873}, {\"ngram\": \"scoring\", \"from\": 3877, \"to\": 3884}, {\"ngram\": \"first-team\", \"from\": 3924, \"to\": 3934}, {\"ngram\": \"all-Atlantic\", \"from\": 3935, \"to\": 3947}, {\"ngram\": \"a two-time team\", \"from\": 3967, \"to\": 3982}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In Hovasse's final season, Penn State went 20-12, reached the Atlantic 10 title game and made the NIT Tournament.\", \"from\": 3989, \"to\": 4102, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4016, \"end\": 4026, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penn_State_Nittany_Lions_basketball\", \"score\": 0.9999988761252956, \"rank\": 7.416176123642831e-07, \"text\": \"Penn State\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penn_State_Nittany_Lions_basketball\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penn_State_Nittany_Lions_basketball\"}, {\"begin\": 4087, \"end\": 4101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Invitation_Tournament\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0819478289194168e-20, \"text\": \"NIT Tournament\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Invitation_Tournament\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Invitation_Tournament\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hovasse's final season\", \"from\": 3992, \"to\": 4014}, {\"ngram\": \"the Atlantic 10 title game\", \"from\": 4047, \"to\": 4073}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That helped set the foundation of Penn State's next three seasons, when the team averaged 22 wins, made two NIT Tournaments and upset fourth-seeded UCLA in the 1991 NCAA Tournament.\", \"from\": 4103, \"to\": 4284, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4137, \"end\": 4147, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penn_State_Nittany_Lions_basketball\", \"score\": 0.9999988761252956, \"rank\": 7.416176123642831e-07, \"text\": \"Penn State\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penn_State_Nittany_Lions_basketball\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penn_State_Nittany_Lions_basketball\"}, {\"begin\": 4211, \"end\": 4226, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Invitation_Tournament\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NIT Tournaments\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Invitation_Tournament\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Invitation_Tournament\"}, {\"begin\": 4251, \"end\": 4255, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UCLA_Bruins_football\", \"score\": 0.6508387769871973, \"rank\": 0.53596430566117, \"text\": \"UCLA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UCLA_Bruins_football\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UCLA_Bruins_football\"}, {\"begin\": 4263, \"end\": 4283, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1991_NCAA_Division_I_Men's_Basketball_Tournament\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.0133300864934574e-16, \"text\": \"1991 NCAA Tournament\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1991_NCAA_Division_I_Men's_Basketball_Tournament\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1991_NCAA_Division_I_Men's_Basketball_Tournament\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the foundation\", \"from\": 4119, \"to\": 4133}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 4175, \"to\": 4183}, {\"ngram\": \"22 wins\", \"from\": 4193, \"to\": 4200}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was very demanding,\\\" Parkhill said.\", \"from\": 4286, \"to\": 4324, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Parkhill\", \"from\": 4310, \"to\": 4318}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We were in a situation where, in order for our guys to win, they had to play at such a high level.\", \"from\": 4325, \"to\": 4424, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a situation\", \"from\": 4337, \"to\": 4348}, {\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 4359, \"to\": 4364}, {\"ngram\": \"our guys\", \"from\": 4369, \"to\": 4377}, {\"ngram\": \"such a high level\", \"from\": 4406, \"to\": 4423}]}, {\"sentence\": \"... With Tom, I really felt that if he had another year of weight training [by redshirting], he would be even better than he was.\", \"from\": 4425, \"to\": 4554, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tom\", \"from\": 4434, \"to\": 4437}, {\"ngram\": \"another year\", \"from\": 4468, \"to\": 4480}, {\"ngram\": \"weight training\", \"from\": 4484, \"to\": 4499}, {\"ngram\": \"redshirting\", \"from\": 4504, \"to\": 4515}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I totally understand where he was coming from.\\\"\", \"from\": 4555, \"to\": 4606, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Over time, of course, they became \\\"great friends,\\\" as Hovasse said, though Parkhill did not necessarily see his former star following him into coaching.\", \"from\": 4608, \"to\": 4760, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 4613, \"to\": 4617}, {\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 4622, \"to\": 4628}, {\"ngram\": \"great friends\", \"from\": 4643, \"to\": 4656}, {\"ngram\": \"Hovasse\", \"from\": 4662, \"to\": 4669}, {\"ngram\": \"Parkhill\", \"from\": 4683, \"to\": 4691}, {\"ngram\": \"his former star\", \"from\": 4716, \"to\": 4731}, {\"ngram\": \"coaching\", \"from\": 4751, \"to\": 4759}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But there were a few signs.\", \"from\": 4761, \"to\": 4788, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a few signs\", \"from\": 4776, \"to\": 4787}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"His feel for the game is very impressive,\\\" Parkhill said.\", \"from\": 4790, \"to\": 4848, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His feel\", \"from\": 4791, \"to\": 4799}, {\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 4804, \"to\": 4812}, {\"ngram\": \"Parkhill\", \"from\": 4834, \"to\": 4842}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Some guys are mechanical, and some guys have a feel for when to make a play, when to push it a little bit.\", \"from\": 4849, \"to\": 4956, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Some guys\", \"from\": 4850, \"to\": 4859}, {\"ngram\": \"some guys\", \"from\": 4880, \"to\": 4889}, {\"ngram\": \"a feel\", \"from\": 4895, \"to\": 4901}, {\"ngram\": \"a play\", \"from\": 4919, \"to\": 4925}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those are the instinctual things you can not really teach.\", \"from\": 4957, \"to\": 5015, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the instinctual things\", \"from\": 4967, \"to\": 4989}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And he did have that.\", \"from\": 5016, \"to\": 5037, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Plus, his personality.\", \"from\": 5038, \"to\": 5060, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Plus, his personality\", \"from\": 5038, \"to\": 5059}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tom's an engaging guy and he's really funny.\", \"from\": 5061, \"to\": 5105, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tom's an engaging guy\", \"from\": 5061, \"to\": 5082}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He has an unbelievable sense of humor.\\\"\", \"from\": 5106, \"to\": 5145, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an unbelievable sense\", \"from\": 5113, \"to\": 5134}, {\"ngram\": \"humor\", \"from\": 5138, \"to\": 5143}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hovasse also is a skilled motivator, which Parkhill saw first-hand.\", \"from\": 5147, \"to\": 5214, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hovasse\", \"from\": 5147, \"to\": 5154}, {\"ngram\": \"a skilled motivator\", \"from\": 5163, \"to\": 5182}, {\"ngram\": \"Parkhill\", \"from\": 5190, \"to\": 5198}, {\"ngram\": \"first-hand\", \"from\": 5203, \"to\": 5213}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Parkhill attended a Japan-U.S. exhibition game before the Tokyo Olympics and marveled at how intensely the Japanese women played for their coach.\", \"from\": 5215, \"to\": 5360, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Parkhill\", \"from\": 5215, \"to\": 5223}, {\"ngram\": \"a Japan-U.S. exhibition game\", \"from\": 5233, \"to\": 5261}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 5269, \"to\": 5287}, {\"ngram\": \"the Japanese women\", \"from\": 5318, \"to\": 5336}, {\"ngram\": \"their coach\", \"from\": 5348, \"to\": 5359}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cAfter the game [Hovasse] said, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0098If I asked them to, they would run the stairs to the roof up and back for 15-20 minutes,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Parkhill said.\", \"from\": 5362, \"to\": 5508, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 5371, \"to\": 5379}, {\"ngram\": \"Hovasse\", \"from\": 5381, \"to\": 5388}, {\"ngram\": \"the stairs\", \"from\": 5434, \"to\": 5444}, {\"ngram\": \"the roof\", \"from\": 5448, \"to\": 5456}, {\"ngram\": \"15-20 minutes\", \"from\": 5473, \"to\": 5486}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Parkhill\", \"from\": 5487, \"to\": 5502}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cAnd they would have.\", \"from\": 5509, \"to\": 5532, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That team had a great work ethic.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Hovasse said there is plenty of Parkhill and Penn State in the way he coaches.\", \"from\": 5533, \"to\": 5649, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5616, \"end\": 5626, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penn_State_Nittany_Lions_basketball\", \"score\": 0.9999988761252956, \"rank\": 7.416176123642831e-07, \"text\": \"Penn State\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penn_State_Nittany_Lions_basketball\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penn_State_Nittany_Lions_basketball\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That team\", \"from\": 5533, \"to\": 5542}, {\"ngram\": \"a great work\", \"from\": 5547, \"to\": 5559}, {\"ngram\": \"Hovasse\", \"from\": 5570, \"to\": 5577}, {\"ngram\": \"plenty\", \"from\": 5592, \"to\": 5598}, {\"ngram\": \"Parkhill\", \"from\": 5602, \"to\": 5610}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 5629, \"to\": 5636}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A lot of people who knew Parkhill and Penn State basketball, even though the game has changed, could see it,\\\" Hovasse said.\", \"from\": 5651, \"to\": 5775, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5690, \"end\": 5700, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penn_State_Nittany_Lions_basketball\", \"score\": 0.9999988761252956, \"rank\": 7.416176123642831e-07, \"text\": \"Penn State\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penn_State_Nittany_Lions_basketball\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penn_State_Nittany_Lions_basketball\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A lot\", \"from\": 5652, \"to\": 5657}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 5661, \"to\": 5667}, {\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 5725, \"to\": 5733}, {\"ngram\": \"Hovasse\", \"from\": 5762, \"to\": 5769}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The way we are a 3-point shooting team, the way we spread the court, and our defense and the way we get after it reminded everybody of Parkhill's basketball.\", \"from\": 5776, \"to\": 5934, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\\"The way\", \"from\": 5776, \"to\": 5784}, {\"ngram\": \"a 3-point shooting team\", \"from\": 5792, \"to\": 5815}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 5817, \"to\": 5824}, {\"ngra